      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "# Flux Guidance - prompt adherence, higher the value, less creativity\n\n\n\n\n\n\n# Batch size: Number of images per batch - Will increase VRAM\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n# Random Noise: Set the control after generate to fixed to test on same seed number when experimenting with prompts.\nChange to randomize for variety.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n# Sampler_name: Affects how the image is denoised. Changing this can give variations in final output.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n# Scheduler: Affects how denoising algorithm. \n\n# Steps: over how long will the denoising takes place. \nGenerally, more steps -> higher quality -> longer time (Don't go too high, will introduce artifacts.)"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": {
